title: Asparagus Noodle Stir Fry
ingredients: ['225g cellophane noodles', '1 teaspoon sesame oil', '2 tablespoons soy sauce', '2 teaspoons caster sugar', '1 tablespoon vegetable oil', '2 cloves garlic, finely chopped', '125g thinly sliced onions', '2 carrots, cut into matchsticks', '225g asparagus, thinly sliced', '3 spring onions cut into 2.5cm pieces', '30g dried shiitake mushrooms, soaked until soft, then sliced into strips', '1 tablespoon sesame seeds', '1 1/2 teaspoons sesame oil']
